title: The Real Joe Biden Story isnt Pretty # 966 (Ep 966)
description:
In this episode I address the Joe Biden campaign announcement for President and the many scandals he’ll have to deal with. I also address the key question being left out of the debate about Spygate scandal. News Picks:
Joe Biden jumps in the Presidential race.
 
Disgraced former FBI Director Jim Comey donated thousands to this Democrat presidential candidate. 
 
Bernie Sanders’ insane new plan would allow 183,000 convicted murderers to vote from prison. 
 
Unsurprisingly, it looks like the “Trump tapes” rumor was nonsense the entire time.
